PROJECT TITLE:
   AI Powered Smart Student Assistant Chatbot System 

   
PROJECT OBJECTIVES :
 * To develop an AI-powered chatbot that assists students with academic information.
 * To provide quick and accurate answers to student queries.
 * To help students access study materials, timetables, and academic updates easily.
 * To reduce the time spent searching for educational information.
 * To improve student learning through personalized assistance.
 * To provide 24/7 support for students anytime and anywhere.
 * To create a user-friendly platform for efficient communication and information access.
 * To enhance the overall educational experience using Artificial Intelligence.

TECHNOLOGY :
         FOR FRONTEND = HTML ,JavaScript 
         FOR BACKEND = python , Node.js
         Database = MySQL,Mongodb

 ADVANTAGE:
     
    * Provides 24/7 student support.
    * Gives quick and instant responses.
    * Easy access to academic information.
    * Saves time and effort for students.
    * Improves learning and productivity.
    * Reduces workload on faculty and administrative staff.
    * User-friendly and accessible from anywhere.


DISADVANTAGE:

    * Depends on internet connectivity.
    * May provide incorrect answers for complex queries.
    * Requires regular updates and maintenance.
    * Cannot fully replace human guidance.
    * Data privacy and security concerns may arise.
    * Development and maintenance can be costly.
    * Limited understanding of highly specific or ambiguous questions.
